{"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdbmhash","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This algorithm was created for sdbm (a public-domain reimplementation of ndbm) database library.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"it was found to do well in scrambling bits, causing better distribution of the keys and fewer splits.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"it also happens to be a good general hashing function with good distribution.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the actual function is hash(i) = hash(i - 1) * 65599 + str[i];","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"what is included below is the faster version used in gawk.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[there is even a faster, duff-device version] the magic prime constant 65599 (2^6 + 2^16 - 1)","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was picked out of thin air while experimenting with many different constants."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this is one of the algorithms used in berkeley db (see sleepycat) and elsewhere."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Hashed string","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"SwiftExtras","relatedModules":["Swift"]}],"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdbmhash","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"extendedModule":"Swift","roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:SS11SwiftExtrasE8sdbmhashSivp","title":"sdbmhash","symbolKind":"property"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String\/sdbmhash","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras","doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift","doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string\/sdbmhash"]}],"references":{"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift/String":{"title":"String","type":"topic","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string","fragments":[{"text":"extension","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"String","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift","role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"title":"Swift","url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras","title":"SwiftExtras","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras","abstract":[],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift/String/sdbmhash":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String\/sdbmhash","url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string\/sdbmhash","type":"topic","title":"sdbmhash","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Hashed string"}],"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdb